    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h4 id="redundant-modifiers">Redundant Modifiers</h4>

<blockquote>
  <p><strong>end</strong> result</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Result must be the end, the <strong>end</strong> is useless here.</p>

